OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FWidespread
OL,6,Fand at times heavy rain will spread
OL,7,Fnorthwards across much of England and
OL,8,FWales, with conditions becoming drier
OL,9,Flater in the far south. Cloudy across
OL,10,FScotland, with showers across Northern
OL,11,FIreland, these slowly easing.
OL,12,FRemaining mild overnight.
