OL,15,Fnorthwards, this lingering across
OL,16,Fnorthern England. Sunshine and
OL,17,Fshowers, locally heavy, breaking out
OL,18,Fin the south with the driest and
OL,19,Fbrightest conditions across the
OL,20,Fnorthern Scotland.
